node_5.subject: Abigail Chen
node_5.description: This is Abigail Chen's plan for Monday February 13: wake up and complete the morning routine at 8:00 am, have breakfast at the Hobb Cafe at 9:00 am, get to know the other participants in the Love Ville program from 10:00 am to 12:00 pm, have a lunch at 12:00 pm, explore the Ville Village and its facilities from 1:00 to 5:00 pm, have dinner at the Hobb Cafe at 6:00 pm, socialize and interact with the other participants from 7:00 to 10:00 pm, reflect on the day's experiences and journal from 10:00 to 11:30 pm, prepare for bed at 11:30 pm, and.
